social_posts.post_text: Big Redd , Not the Lil One ❤️

A moment💕 !! I’m just going to sit this here and have a lil story time with yall!! Look at me, just a little ole cali girl from Fillmore who Came here 14 years ago with my 1 lil suit case, hopes and no dreams yet! But once I hit the streets I seen so many opportunities my dreams & goals changed. The streets open my eyes to many possibilities and opportunities that showed me anything is possible and that I could be my own boss one day! Starting off as a college student you don’t know which way to start, so vulnerable, naive and anxious to get money and be grown lol … i was eager to be successful but it pushed me in a way, i wouldn’t regret but i wouldn’t suggest it to anyone either… so boom now here I am Stripping, getting all this money becoming distracted from my goals. All this money with no purpose still made no sense to me, I wanted more! 
But i got pregnant, fell in love so now my options became limited from what i always knew. Left the strip club and stepped out on FAITH, got into oil and gas, literally became a slave to a asian lady. I thought “ this can’t be the way I’m supposed to live”. My now husband (#noighubby) said fuck them bae “i got you, go after your dreams” which at the time i thought was makeup.. did that for a 1 year or  two, became good at that then i got bored and tired of the attitudes from that industry… 
THEN BARTENDING… I didn’t know much about liquor but I could whip up some good drinks. Taught myself how to bartend with no school (was to expensive), Took advantage of all the bar education around me in the club industry (thank you @vipkim_ ), to soon become a bar manager, to general manager (thank you @yakiniog), to now me teaching young women how to bartend and create a career for themselves & make great money doing it! Im honored that GOD is using me in this way, it feels like my purpose. If i can help even just 1 girl avoid all the crazy and BS in life that we women have to deal with I’m ok with that… but to be able to touch 10+ girls is crazy goals to me! 

I want to thank everyone who supports me in any way, pushes me, and is just there to see me through, I REALLYY REALLLYY APPRECIATE YALL!! 

📷 @two3films

If you’ve been searching for bartending courses, Set the bar bartending teaches a hands-on technique class. This isn’t your ordinary bartending school; this is the charm school of bartending schools.

Having the best bartenders is one of the most crucial factors that determine a bars success. There are details behind the bottles you will learn in this course. This course will give you the knowledge to feel confident to join the bosses of one of the world's most respected professions, one with never a dull moment. Need extra income, help with school loans, or just life, bartending can help when done right. 
Beginners to professionals, what you really need to know to get to the bag and develop your bar crafts will be instructed in my courses. It will include content such as drink & bar knowledge, attire & appearances, customer service, organization & time, tips& sales, behind the bar training & so much more. I'm excited to teach you all some of my fun secrets. I also offer job placement once certified (depending on your skill set & hustle).💕

📝Sign up for my next class SEPTEMBER 10, 2023
